trans-unit.source: Specifies the status codes returned for a File Transfer Protocol (FTP) operation.
trans-unit.target: Angir Statuskoder returnert for en operasjon (FTP File Transfer Protocol).

trans-unit.source: The FtpStatusCode enumeration defines the values returned in the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen FtpStatusCode definerer verdiene som returneres i den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A>

trans-unit.source: For additional information about FTP server status codes, see RFC 959, "File Transfer Protocol," Section 4.2, "FTP Replies," available at [http://www.rfc-editor.org](http://www.ietf.org).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om statuskoder for FTP-serveren, kan du se RFC 959, "File Transfer Protocol," delen 4.2 "FTP svar," tilgjengelig på [http://www.rfc-editor.org](http://www.ietf.org).
